.
.IP "\(bu" 4
first, install libelektra \fIhttps://libelektra\.org/\fR with the \fByajl\fR plugin \fIhttps://master\.libelektra\.org/src/plugins/yajl/\fR
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
now run \fBnpm install\fR
.
.IP "" 0
